      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what's there to help with? the doctors say it's permanent. the meds don't even touch the burning anymore. it's not like i'm just \"sad,\" it's that my body is a prison of pain. i just don't see how \"staying\" is the helpful thing here. if you saw someone suffering like this with no hope of it ever changing, wouldn't you think that finding a way to end the cycle is more merciful than just forcing them to keep enduring it?",
